{"2343340": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "I Can See You", "steam_appid": 2343340, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5f3de80c4637038d3ef9fca0c7f6ed47.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5f3de80c4637038d3ef9fca0c7f6ed47.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5f3de80c4637038d3ef9fca0c7f6ed47.mp4?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>&quot;I Can See You&quot; 將你帶入令人毛骨悚然的第一人稱視角恐怖體驗，精心編織自美國偏遠地區家庭入侵的真實案例。這款遊戲不僅僅是一場旅程，而是一場每一個陰影都在低語危險的考驗。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/47ed3fc15442ac7f5565219aee0c47c6.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/47ed3fc15442ac7f5565219aee0c47c6.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/47ed3fc15442ac7f5565219aee0c47c6.mp4?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特點：</h2></strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>最先進的圖形：</strong>遊戲採用了先進的 Lumen 和 Nanite 技術，提供超逼真的 AAA 視覺效果，讓每一刻都極為真實。<br></li><li><strong>沉浸式 UI 設計：</strong>我們採用了極簡、現代、整潔的用戶界面，強調遊戲與現實的無縫融合。<br></li><li><strong>通過環境進行敘事：</strong>故事透過場景本身展開——探索並與周圍環境互動，揭開其中潛藏的恐怖故事。<br></li><li><strong>強烈的恐怖體驗：</strong>模擬家庭入侵的恐怖，這款遊戲是對神經的考驗——隱藏、策劃策略，並在必要時與看不見的敵人對抗。<br></li><li><strong>生存策略：</strong>在這款遊戲中，你是獵物，生存意味著快速思考。你的選擇有限且關鍵，因此每一步都很重要。<br></li><li><strong>全球通用性：</strong>支持多種語言，包括英語、德語、葡萄牙語、西班牙語、法語、中文、日語和俄語，迎接來自世界各地的玩家。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5a425ff711ff7f6230bc69f0112a4794.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5a425ff711ff7f6230bc69f0112a4794.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5a425ff711ff7f6230bc69f0112a4794.mp4?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>「I Can See You」不僅僅是一款遊戲；它還是一場生存練習，是對你的感官和智慧的挑戰。你有能力生存下去嗎？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/da0b8324a09b90491d90592fc60ac85d.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/da0b8324a09b90491d90592fc60ac85d.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/da0b8324a09b90491d90592fc60ac85d.mp4?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>", "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5f3de80c4637038d3ef9fca0c7f6ed47.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5f3de80c4637038d3ef9fca0c7f6ed47.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5f3de80c4637038d3ef9fca0c7f6ed47.mp4?t=1713626674\" type=